'''Sekhukhune''' goba '''Matsebe Sekhukhune''', (1814–1882), ebe ele ngwana wa mathomo go ba bararo ba kgoshi Sekwati le Thorometjane. Barwa ba Kgoši Sekwati ke Sekhukhune (Matsebe), Dinkwanyane le Kgoloko. Ka setjo sa Bapedi bogoši bo tjea ka ngwana wa pele ka morago ga lehu la tatagwe. Matsebe (Sekhukhune) o rile ka morago ga lehu la tatagwe (Sekwati) ka 1861, a latela setjo sa sepedi ka ge Tatagwe e be ele kgoši. O thopile bogoši go morwarragwe Mampuru ka lerumo. Mampuru yeo lehono baretjego (Pretoria Central Prison) ka yena, e be e le morwarrago Sekhukhune ka ge mmagwe (Kgomomakatane) a nyetjwe ke bakgomana ba ga Sekwati. Mampuru o godišitjwe ke mmago Sekhukhune (Thorometjane) ka lapeng la mošate.

Ge Hendrik Potgieter le masole a gagwe (Voortrekkers) ba sahlela mošate wa bapedi ka pširing ka 1838. Sekwati o ba fentje mara a tla a lemoga gore mošate wa gagwe wa pširing ga se wa bolokega ke ge a tlo khudugela Thaba Bošego (Leolo).

Sekhukhune I, ebe ele kgoši kgolo ya [[Bapedi]] (goba Marota) ba ga [[Sekhukhune]], [[Limpopo]] nageng ya [[Afrika Borwa]]. O be a dula ko thabeng ya Leolo,<ref>{{cite book|last = du Plessis|first = E.J. |coauthors = |title = Suid-Afrikaanse berg- en rivier name|publisher = Tafelberg-uitgewers, Cape Town |year = 1973|pages = 187|isbn = 0-624-00273-X}}</ref> e ago kgona go e šireletja. Kgoši kgolo Sekhukhune naga ya gagwe e thoma ka noka ya Lekwe, south ([[Vaal River]]), go fihla ka noka ya Lebepe, north (Limpopo River) gape Mogomatse, east (Komati River) le kgalagadi, west (Bophirima). Sechaba sa Bapedi sebopa ke mehlobo ya Batau (Manganeng, Masemola, Mogashoa), Bakgaga (Mphahlele, Kopa, Maake), Baroka (Malatjie, Ratau, Mashishi, Phasa), Bakwena, Bakone (Matlala), Moletlane le babangwe. Magoši a ga Sekhukhune ka Palo 167 le Dintona tje 268. 

Ba bodikela (Makgowa) barile ge bafihla mo nageng ya ga Sekhukhune ba e abaganya Kage babe banyaka mahumo a naga (gauta) babe baerela leina la Transvaal, ge go fihla maisemane ba e a abaganya gape ba e bitja PWV (Pretoria, Witwatersrand le Vereeniging). Kgoši kgolo Sekhukhune o lwetje naga ya gagwe goba go fihla Maburu le Maisemane ba kopana ba dira seboka gore ba kgone goka fenya Sekhukhune.

Sekhukhune o kgonne go fenya ntwa magareng ga Maburu le Maesimane bale seboka. Goba go fihla Maburu le Maisemane ba eya gohloma seboka sesengwe le Maswatsi ke ge ba kgona go moswara ba moisha ko toronkong ya Pitori (Tshwane).

Leshika la kgoro ya Sekhukhune.

